lead_paragraph: Alex Romero, Jose Martinez and Sandy Leon drove in runs to lead Venezuela's Aragua Tigers over Cuba's Ciego de Avila 3-1 Thursday and advance to the Caribbean Series semifinals.

headline.print_headline: Venezuela Beats Cuba 3-1, Reaches Caribbean Series Semis
